    "Retrieval-based methods personalize model outputs by incorporating user-specific information retrieved at inference time (Dai et al., 2023; Kang et al., 2023; Liu et al., 2023; Wang et al., 2023; Zhiyuli et al., 2023; Salemi et al., 2024)."
